    v0 = tmp
    v0 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.24 * tmp + 0.63) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.54)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.33 + tmp + 0.67)) - wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.01)))
    v1 = wp.exp((v1 + (v0 + 0.94 * v2 + 0.00)))
    data[tid] = v0
